Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,篮球后卫的几率有多大啊?\Nthat I am gonna meet a point guard named Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 那我能不能至少加入你们呀?\NWell, can I at least join you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 听着 听着 我来当你的恋爱指导吧\NMnh. Listen, listen. I'll be your wingman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 你是有史以来最烂的指导\NNo. No, you are the worst wingman ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 哎...约翰 这很有趣吧?\NYes. Just... John, this is fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 我真不该和彭妮出去玩\NTo be honest, I usually never go out with Penny
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为所有可爱的帅哥都跟她回家而不是我\N'cause all the cute guys always go home with her instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思不是她和很多帅哥回了家\NI mean, not that she goes home with a lot of dudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-她不淫荡 但是她也没那么规矩啦 -恩哼\N- She's not slutty, but she's not a prude either. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 她对性方面的好奇心还是很健康的\NIn conclusion, she has a very healthy sexual curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-你怎么回事?-是谁推介你报这个班的呀?\N- What's wrong with you? - So who turned you on to the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我老婆 额 是前妻\NUh, my wife. Well, ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哇奥 这是我第一次这么说...\NWow. That's the first time I've said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-前妻 -真抱歉 你们刚分手吗?\N- Ex-wife. - I'm so sorry. Did you just split?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,额 是的 大约是一个月前\NWell, it was, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是 很长时间了 恩\Na month ago. Like, a long time ago. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是阿莱克斯店的后门\NThis is the back door to Alex's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很快 很简单 超便捷\NReal quick, real simple, simple B&E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哇嚓!老兄 你在搞毛啊?\NWhoa! Man, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我该怎么做 扎克 布莱夫?敲门吗?\NWhat do you want me to do, Zach Braff? Knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我有钥匙的呀 老兄\NI got the keys, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,额 那就不是超便捷了\NWell, then it's not a B&E.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胳膊甚至都够不着\NYour arm's not even gonna reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我能够得着 我胳膊挺壮的...\NYes, it is. I have huge arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你够不着\NNo, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-特别是右手 -你这暴龙的手臂\N- Especially the right one. - You got t-Rex arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,戴夫\NDave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我啥也没找着\NI can't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的尺码都在这了\NAre all the sizes out on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,或者阿莱克斯在后面还藏了更多?\Nor does Alex have any more in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,去查查看电脑!\NJust go to the computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 看看这个\NDude, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,波 班瑟斯基\NBo Bazinski.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我们要找的人 湖畔广告\NThat's our man. Lakeshore Advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好亲我吧 他家的地址在这呢\NGet ready to French my mouth. His home address is on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道他住在西部\NI didn't realize he lived on western.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个住在那边的男友 他是个摩托党\NI had a boyfriend who lived there. He's in a biker gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 额 我们不用这么做\NYou know, uh, we don't have to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想做的话\Nif you don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就告诉我一件事...\NJust tell me one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况下 席格会怎么做?\NWhat would Seagal do in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,额 我觉得这真是老一套\NWell, I think it's pretty cut and dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他会乘着老鹰光速飞到 波的家里\NHe'd fly over to Bo's house on an eagle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,从窗口跳进去 撕开他的喉咙\Nleap through the front window, tear his throat out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把它当做一个捉梦器\Nuse it as a dream catcher,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后骑着一只北极熊闪人\Nand then ride away on a polar bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再告诉我一件事\NJust tell me one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想知道事实吗?-我想知道事实\N- Do you want the truth? - I want the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不能接受事实! -你定了红色代码吗?\N- You can't handle the truth! - Did you order the code red?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的太对了 我定了!\NYou're damn right, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做?\NWhy is that something that you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只是觉得该这么做呗 走吧\NIt just feels right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来玩个游戏吧\NLet's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们五年以后是什么样的?\NWhere do you see us in five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个游戏吗? 额\NIs that a game? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的食物呢?\NWhere is our food?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 回答问题啊 亲爱的\NCome on. Answer the question, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 五年计划\NAll right, 5-year plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,额 我想想...更漂亮的房子\NUh, let's see... nicer house,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,更好的车 有孩子\Nnicer car, kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许机器人在那时候也是个不错的选项\Nmaybe a robot if that's an option by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 菜来了 奥 不勒个是吧!\NOkay, here we go. Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在我们二十分钟后才到这的\NThey got here, like, 20 minutes after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这完全是因为我们是黑人和金发妞的组合\NThis is totally 'cause we're black on blonde.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你完全没把我的话放在心上\NOkay, you're not taking this seriously at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么放在心上 啊?\NTaking what seriously, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你问的这些荒谬的宇宙问题是在坑爹吧?\NThis ridiculous "Cosmo" quiz you're walking me through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没觉得这很荒谬 我希望我们\NI don't think it's ridiculous that I want us to be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,永远在一起 而且能葬在一起\Ntogether forever and get buried next to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有棵树会长在我俩的墓中央\Nand that maybe a tree will grow between our grave
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两个孩子会在树下拥有他们的初吻\Nand that two kids will have their first kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道对你来说也荒谬吗?\Nunder that tree. Does that sound ridiculous to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是荒谬\NYeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么两个孩子要在墓地里接吻?\NWhy are the two kids kissing in a graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道!也许他俩是暮光之城的铁杆粉丝呢\NI don't know! Maybe they're really big "Twilight" fans
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-或者他们只是相爱了 布拉德!-不要啊!\N- or maybe they're just in love, Brad! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的糖醋鸭子!\NMy duck confit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的抱歉 我们真是..\NWe're sorry. We're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道最糟的桥段是什么吗?\NAnd you know what the worst part is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不仅仅失去了你的爱人\NYou're not just losing this person that you've fallen in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你还失去了你最好的朋友 不是吗?\NYou're losing your best friend, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太对了 那当然是我最无法接受的失去\NTotally. That has been the hardest part for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那种感觉就像那个你每晚入睡前都要\Nfor sure. It's like that person that you check in with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他是否安好的人\Nat the end of every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 有时候上帝关了一扇门\NYou know, sometimes God closes a door
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,却打开了...他的心\Nand then he opens... up his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我应该给她打电话?\NMaybe I should call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是该给她打电话?\NShould I call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 这种事情没有该做什么不该做什么\NI don't know. There's no rules in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我要走了\NI'm sorry. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我...不好意思了\NY... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你爱她 你应该让她...管它呢\NIf you love her, you set her...  Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,干的漂亮，傻蛋\NUgh! Way to go, goose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?\NYou ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,波 班瑟斯基 出来单挑!\NBo Bazinski, prepare to meet your maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让你血染大河\NThe river will run red with your blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你脊梁骨抽出来当棍子用!\Nand I will rip your spine out and use it as a loofah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,波 在吗?\NIs Bo here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很久都没有BO得朋友来过了\NBo hasn't had friends over in so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在该怎么办?\NWhat do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈妈在这里我们怎么办?\NHow do we do this with his mom here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管 她最好也看看\NIt doesn't matter. She better get on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我报仇不能等\NMy vengeance knows no age...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这儿 孩子们 玩得开心\NHere we are, boys. Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 B太太 -很高兴见到你\N- Thanks, Mrs. B!  - Great meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 再见\NMm-hmm. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-再见 我可以的 对吗? -当然\N- Bye. I can do this, right? - Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在进去 让我们解决他\NNow get in there. Let's finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好 兄弟\NSweet line, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以...我们就开始吧!\NIf it works... Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法接受真相...\NYou can't handle the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 波? -我认识你们吗?\N- Bo? - Do I know you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得我了? 恩?\NYou don't remember me? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是在微博认识的吗?\NAre we Facebook friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你说的"微博"是他的婚礼\NOh, if by "Facebook" you mean his wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的"朋友" 意思正好相反\Nand by "Friends," you mean "No, the opposite of that word."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-哦天哪 是你 老兄 -对了 老兄\N-Oh, good God. It's you, brah. -That's right, brah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我很长时间来一直想找你谈谈\NI've wanted to talk to you for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了一件很糟糕的是 我真的真的很抱歉\NI did a terrible thing to you, and I am so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 这可没料到\NUh, wasn't expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那看上去很好吃 我要拿这个\NOh, that looks great. I just need to grab this baster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧 他显然还没忘了他老婆\NCome on. He was clearly not over his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该得到更好的男人\NYou deserve so much better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了 今晚不是为了见男人\NBesides, tonight wasn't about meeting guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚是女人夜 不是吗?\NIt was ladies' night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 梅莉蒂絲 維埃拉\NHey, Meredith Vieira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能有多少个女人夜?\Nhow many ladies' nights can you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的一周里 你把我拖去\NIn the last week, you have dragged me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一次空手道和普拉提班 让我试开了一次威姿\Nto a karate pilates class, made me test-drive a Yaris,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还带我去看了一次孩子们演的《毛发》\Nand talked me into seeing a children's production
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地第二幕开场之前被终止了\Nof "Hair," which thankfully, got shut down before the second act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 那参观安德鲁 洛伊 韦伯 旧居呢?\NOkay, wait. What about the tour of Andrew Lloyd Webber's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢那个\NYou loved that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是弗兰克 劳埃德 赖特旧居\NIt was a Frank Lloyd Wright house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我一点都不喜欢\Nand no, I didn't love it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不停地问导游\N'cause you kept asking the tour guide
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪间房间里写了 歌剧魅影\Nwhich room he wrote "Phantom of the Opera" in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他一直不告诉我（因为不是那个人写的）\N'Cause he wouldn't give me an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是因为你想和我玩\NThis is so not about you wanting to hang out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为你无法承受\NOkay, this about you not being able to handle the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你分手了你很孤独的事实 这没什么\Nthat you're alone since your breakup, and that's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是麻烦你承认这一点以及不要再拖我去那些\Nbut please just admit it and stop dragging me along
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的活动了 我们呆在家里\Non these terrible activities. We should've just stayed home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-看 "单身汉"就好了 -我把这个放回来\N-  and watched "The Bachelor." - And to put the baster back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！\NGet out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你说你想谈谈 那就谈谈\NLook, you say you wanna talk. Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...我不想像阿莱克斯和戴夫一样\NI just... I-I don't want to end up like Alex and Dave, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把彼此看得那么理所应当\Nand take each other for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 宝贝 别这样\NOh, babe, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莱克斯和戴夫的问题不是因为\NAlex and Dave's problems had nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,留还是走\Nwith staying in or going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,关键不是你在哪里 而是你和谁在一起\NIt's not about where you are. It's who you're with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好着呢!\NWe're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗?\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 虽然饿死了\NI mean, starving,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但很幸福\Nbut good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你的一切\NI love everything about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你打喷嚏时候那种可怕的表情\Neven that scary little face you make when you sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我打喷嚏的时候表情不可怕\NI do not make a scary face when I sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有啦 你是我认识的唯一这样的人\N- You do. You're the only person I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的? -谁打喷嚏睁着眼睛的?\N- Oh, really? - who sneezes with their eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就像...哎楸！\NYou're like... ah-choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哎楸！\NAh-choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看 我们不是戴夫和阿莱克斯\NLook, we're not Dave and Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是布莱妮和简德\NWe're Brane and Jad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 好 我们先得把你肚子塞饱\NWait. Okay. We need to get food in you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们是简德和布莱 -好吧\N-We're Jad and bran. -okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为阿莱克斯是我一生的爱 兄弟\NI thought Alex was the love of my life, brah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,结果她认为我就是"那个帮她从直接邮寄广告\NTurns out she thought I was just "That guy who helped her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在当地拉生意的人"\Nwith her direct mail campaign to local businesses."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知所措了 我觉得就像失去了一切\NI don't know, man. I just feel like I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这种感觉\NI know the feeling, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你能按原计划行事吗 戴夫?\NWill you stick to the plan, Dave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是阿莱克斯做了选择\NBut Alex made her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 你得向前走\NYou know, you gotta move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都应该\NWe both do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一个智者曾经告诉我\NA wise man once told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"你不能关注于你有的东西\N"You can't focus on all the stuff that you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而应该专注于你有的有意义的新东西"\NYou gotta focus on all the cool new stuff that you have."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对 我想也许是我小时候 很小的时候\NYou're right. You know, I guess it's because my dad left us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲离开了\Nwhen... when I was real young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在找爱 就好像 用来\NI've always been searching for love, to, like, fill
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,填补我内心的空洞...啊！\Nthat dark void that... aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才要打我!啊！\NDid you just "Hi-yucka" me? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄!打他鼻梁?\NDude! Hi-yucka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做布拉夫 你就做\NYou can be Braff all you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我一直是 席格\Nbut I'm Seagal all the time, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近看见席格了吗?\NHave you seen Seagal recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他看上去像马里奥 巴塔利\NHe looks like Mario Batali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我手腕好痛 -得了吧 马科斯\N- I hurt my wrist so bad! - Come on, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要吐了 我要吐出来了\NI'm gonna throw up. I'm gonna puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,马科斯 把持好你自己 行不行?\NMax, get yourself together, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈！-你甚至没打到他\N-Hyah! You didn't even hit the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哼! 呀！呜！\NHuh! Yah! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷！嗷！嘿老兄！\NOw! Ow! Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,停下！停下！\NHey! Abort! Abort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉！抱歉！我的 呃...\NSorry! Sorry! My, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呃！啊！\NUhh! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听着...\NListen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我为我说过的话道歉 我不是故意的\NI'm sorry about what I said. I didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是故意的 但是说得对\NYes, you did, but you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗? -是啊\N- I was? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是把你拖来拖去\NI mean, I've been dragging you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把你当做戴夫的替代品\Ntreating you like my replacement Dave,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是十年了 我一直没有孤单过\Nbut I haven't been alone in, like, ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要崩溃了！ - 不是这样 阿莱\N- and I'm freaking out! - Come on, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不孤单好吗? 你有我们\NOkay, you're not alone. Okay? You have all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只是...你真的需要选点好活动\NIt's just... you really gotta edit your activity choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说的对 -好了?\N- You're right. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然 公平地说\NAlthough, in fairness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,威姿这车很划算\Nthat Yaris was a lot of car for the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好朋友很难找\NGood friends are really hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们随时随地都支持你 哪怕你是错的\NThey gotta be there for you, even when you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但同时\NBut at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不能只告诉你你想听的\Nthey can't just tell you what you wanna hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还得告诉你\NThey've also gotta be willing to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道的\Nwhat you need to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为什么真爱这么难找\NThat's the real reason true love's so hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为爱的基础是友谊\NBecause the basis of love is friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且真正的友谊很难很难找\Nand friendship is really, really rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那就是为什么我把我的第二支玫瑰\NSo that's why I'm giving my second rose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,献给我在场最好的朋友\Nto my best friend on the show so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,科尼斯塔 G 你能接受我的爱吗?\NKrista G., will you accept this rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当我和你在一起的时候\NWhen I'm with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 我们在哪儿没关系\Nbabe, it doesn't matter where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上过的够呛啊?\NRough night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没事\NNo, it was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢?\NYou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好 有个很有趣的厨师...\NI was all right. There was this really funny chef...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 闭嘴\NHey, zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 桐亚 B要把玫瑰哭湿了\NI mean, Tonya B.'s getting hosed out of a rose over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很专心 - 好吧 我希望你意识到\N- I'm invested. - Okay, I hope you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,桐亚 B根本没一直陪着他\Nthat Tonya B. was not even there for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她和他一起去了豪华房间\NShe went to the fantasy suite with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-去发生关系 -去做爱\N- To have sex with him. - To make love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,两者不一样\NIt's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天晚上别让我睡着\NDon't let me fall asleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我有点脑震荡\NI think I have a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在那个混蛋从后面进来 但是他有钥匙\NNow the perp came in through the back, but he had a key,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以肯定是内部人员 有可能是你们认识的人\Nso it was definitely an inside job, probably someone you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 阿莱克斯 我有问题问题...\NSo, Alex, I just got one question for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多了解...呃\NHow well do you know, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人?\NThis guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你兄弟\NI told you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当一个黑人有多难！啊！ 当着你的面！\NIt's way harder to be a black dude. Uhh! In your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当同性恋很容易！ 你闻到了吗?\NBeing a gay dude's easy!  You smell that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 种族歧视\NUgh. Racism.
